<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>AmicBridge – A private bridge between borrowers and lenders</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="AmicBridge is a private peer-to-peer network. We review who is entering, how they present themselves, and how they describe what they want to borrow or lend.">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f5f7;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --text-muted: #6b7280;
      --primary: #2563eb;
      --primary-hover: #1d4ed8;
      --primary-soft: #e0edff;
      --radius-lg: 12px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      --max-width: 1000px;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-main);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    button {
      font-family: inherit;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Header / nav */

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.9rem 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.4rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
    }

    .nav-links a::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -0.12rem;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #2563eb;
      transition: width 0.15s ease-out;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-cta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .nav-cta a {
      color: #2563eb;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .nav-cta .btn-small {
      padding: 0.45rem 0.95rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      background: #ffffff;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .nav-cta .btn-small:hover {
      background: #f3f4f6;
    }

    /* Hero */

    .hero {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
      padding: 3rem 0 3.2rem;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.8rem;
    }

    .hero-text {
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 2.6vw + 1.2rem, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-body {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 1.6rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 0.68rem 1.3rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-hover);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
      padding: 0.68rem 1.3rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f9fafb;
    }

    .hero-footnote {
      margin-top: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 640px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Contact / form */

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .section-text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.4rem 1.4rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .field {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .field label {
      color: #111827;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .field input,
    .field textarea,
    .field select {
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-family: inherit;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .field input:focus,
    .field textarea:focus,
    .field select:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
    }

    .field small {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .form-note {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }

    .form-success {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #166534;
      background: #ecfdf3;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
    }

    .form-success.visible {
      display: block;
    }

    .side-note {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .side-note strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: #f9fafb;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    footer .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    /* Responsive */

    @media (max-width: 880px) {
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero {
        border-radius: 0;
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="shell nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
      <a href="#" class="logo">
        <div class="logo-mark">A</div>
        <div class="logo-text">AmicBridge</div>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#how">How it works</a>
        <a href="#ethics">Trust & identity</a>
        <a href="#borrow">Borrow</a>
        <a href="#lend">Lend</a>
        <a href="#strategy">Strategy</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="nav-cta">
        <a href="#contact">Sign in</a>
        <button class="btn-small" type="button" id="btn-join-nav">Join the network</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="about">
      <div class="shell hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1 class="hero-title">
            A private, trusted bridge between real borrowers and real lenders.
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-body">
            AmicBridge is a private peer-to-peer network. Every member goes through identity checks
            before being allowed into the network, and every request is collected in a clear, structured way.
            Our role is to be the trusted bridge: we review who is entering, how they present themselves,
            and how they describe what they want to borrow or lend.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <button class="btn-primary" type="button" id="btn-request-loan">
              Request a loan
            </button>
            <button class="btn-secondary" type="button" id="btn-offer-lending">
              Offer lending
            </button>
          </div>

          <p class="hero-footnote">
            AmicBridge never holds funds or crypto, never signs loan contracts, and never guarantees repayment,
            returns or matches. All agreements and transfers happen directly between members, who must make their
            own decisions and assessments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Simple "How it works" placeholder (optional) -->
    <section class="section" id="how">
      <div class="shell">
        <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
        <p class="section-text">
          This is a concept-stage outline. In a full product, AmicBridge would:
          verify identities, collect structured loan or lending offers, and provide a private
          environment where members can review each other and agree on their own terms.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact / request form -->
    <section class="section" id="contact">
      <div class="shell">
        <h2 class="section-title">Send a request about borrowing or lending.</h2>
        <p class="section-text">
          Use this form to signal interest in the network, whether you mainly want to borrow, lend, or explore both.
          In a real deployment, this would send your details to the AmicBridge team over a secure channel.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <form id="contact-form" method="post" action="#">
              <div class="field">
                <label for="intent">I am mainly interested in</label>
                <select id="intent" name="intent">
                  <option value="">Select an option</option>
                  <option value="Borrowing">Borrowing</option>
                  <option value="Lending">Lending</option>
                  <option value="Both">Both borrowing and lending</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div class="field">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input id="name" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your full name" required />
              </div>

              <div class="field">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
              </div>

              <div class="field">
                <label for="message">Short description</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us briefly about your situation or what you want to explore." required></textarea>
                <small>This is a concept form only. It does not create an account or any kind of agreement.</small>
              </div>

              <button class="btn-primary" type="submit">Send request</button>
              <div class="form-note">
                Please do not include sensitive personal data (full ID numbers, passwords, etc.) in this message.
              </div>

              <div class="form-success" id="form-success">
                Thank you. Your request has been recorded on this example page.
                In a real implementation, this would be sent securely to the AmicBridge team for follow-up.
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="side-note">
            <strong>What AmicBridge is – and isn’t.</strong>
            <p>
              The idea of AmicBridge is to be a structured, private bridge between people, not a public marketplace and not a bank.
              It would help members present themselves clearly, understand who they are dealing with, and keep a record of what was agreed.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
              Before any real product launches, the concept would need to be adapted to local law and risk rules.
              Members would always be responsible for their own decisions and independent legal or financial advice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <div class="shell footer-inner">
      <div>© <span id="year"></span> AmicBridge. All rights reserved.</div>
      <div>
        <a href="#terms">Terms</a> · <a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>

<script>
  // Year
  document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();

  function goToContact(intentValue) {
    var select = document.getElementById("intent");
    if (select && intentValue) {
      select.value = intentValue;
    }
    var contact = document.getElementById("contact");
    if (contact && contact.scrollIntoView) {
      contact.scrollIntoView({ behavior: "smooth", block: "start" });
    }
  }

  document.getElementById("btn-request-loan")
    .addEventListener("click", function () {
      goToContact("Borrowing");
    });

  document.getElementById("btn-offer-lending")
    .addEventListener("click", function () {
      goToContact("Lending");
    });

  document.getElementById("btn-join-nav")
    .addEventListener("click", function () {
      goToContact("");
    });

  // Fake submit handler for demo
  var form = document.getElementById("contact-form");
  var success = document.getElementById("form-success");

  form.addEventListener("submit", function (e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    success.classList.add("visible");
    // Here you would send the data to your backend in a real deployment.
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
